                            <p>This inscription is dated in the 12th year of <hi rend="bold">Rājanārāyaṇa Śambuvarāja</hi><note>See the introduction of No. 52.</note> and records the setting up of a <hi rend="bold">Jaina</hi> image on <hi rend="bold">Vaigai-Tirumalai</hi>, <hi rend="italic">i.e.</hi>, on the holy mountain of <hi rend="bold">Vaigai</hi>.</p>						
                            
